## Overview

This dashboard analyzes **airport delays across the United States**, focusing on delay frequency, severity, and patterns over time and geography.
The goal is to provide a **clear, high-level view of operational performance** in U.S. airports and support exploratory analysis of delay behavior.

The dashboard was built in **Power BI** with an emphasis on clarity, consistency, and business-oriented insights.

